        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #667eea;">‚úÖ Mood Logged!</h2>
        <p style="color: #666;">Your mood has been successfully recorded.</p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 1.5rem; width: 100%;" onclick="closeModal()">OK</button>
